org.elasticsearch.index

Class NodeServicesProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.elasticsearch.index.NodeServicesProvider

  • public final class NodeServicesProvider
extends java.lang.Object
    Simple provider class that holds the Index and Node level services used by a shard. This is just a temporary solution until we cleaned up index creation and removed injectors on that level as well.
